# Teaching: Hub KB System — Librarian + Gardener Advisors (v1)

**Family:** hub-kb-system
**Version:** 1.0
**Created:** 2026-03-27
**Impact:** 9
**Source Session:** session-20260326-170206
**safe_to_auto_adopt:** false — requires hub-only deployment; review characteristics and adoption_status schema before applying to hub-registry.json

